sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Frontend
    participant APIGW as API Gateway
    participant L1 as Approval Workflow Lambda
    participant SF as Step Functions State Machine
    participant L2 as SNS Notification Lambda
    participant SNS as Amazon SNS
    participant DDB as DynamoDB (WorkflowState)
    participant L3 as Approval Decision Lambda
    participant Reviewer as Human Reviewer
    
    User->>Frontend: Submit high-risk action
    Frontend->>APIGW: POST /approval/start
    APIGW->>L1: Invoke
    
    L1->>SF: StartExecution
    
    Note over SF: State: RecordApprovalRequest
    
    SF->>L2: Invoke with task token
    
    Note over SF: State: WaitForApproval - Workflow PAUSED
    
    L2->>DDB: PutItem - Store task token
    DDB-->>L2: Success
    
    L2->>SNS: Publish notification
    SNS-->>Reviewer: Email/SMS notification
    
    L2-->>SF: Return (workflow paused)
    SF-->>L1: Execution started
    L1-->>APIGW: Return workflow_id
    APIGW-->>Frontend: 200 OK
    Frontend-->>User: Display countdown timer
    
    Note over Reviewer: Reviews and makes decision
    
    Reviewer->>Frontend: Click DENY button
    Frontend->>APIGW: POST /approval/decide
    APIGW->>L3: Invoke
    
    L3->>SF: SendTaskSuccess
    
    Note over SF: State: ProcessDecision - DENY path
    
    Note over SF: State: RecordDenial
    
    SF->>DDB: PutItem - Record decision
    DDB-->>SF: Success
    
    SF-->>L3: Execution completed
    L3-->>APIGW: Return result
    APIGW-->>Frontend: 200 OK
    Frontend-->>User: Display result - ACTION DENIED
    
    Note over User,DDB: Total workflow time: 8.3 seconds
